---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="Get Started ‚Äî TekMoral" 
  description="Schedule a free consultation with our team to discuss your project and how we can help transform your business."
  ogImage="https://www.tekmoral.com/og-get-started.png"
  noIndex={false}
>
  <HeroSection
    title="Let's Build Something Great Together"
    description="Schedule a free consultation with our team. We'll discuss your goals, challenges, and how we can help transform your business with technology."
    badge="Get Started"
    primaryButtonText="Book Now"
    primaryButtonLink="#booking"
  />

  <section id="booking" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <!-- Booking Form -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 text-slate-900">Schedule Your Free Consultation</h2>
        <form action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST" class="space-y-4">
          <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="YOUR_WEB3FORMS_KEY" />
          <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="New Consultation Request from TekMoral" />
          <input type="hidden" name="redirect" value="https://www.tekmoral.com/thank-you" />

          <label class="grid gap-2">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">Name *</span>
            <input class="rounded-md bg-slate-100 border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-slate-900 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-500" name="name" required />
          </label>

          <label class="grid gap-2">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">Email *</span>
            <input class="rounded-md bg-slate-100 border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-slate-900 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-500" type="email" name="email" required />
          </label>

          <label class="grid gap-2">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">Phone</span>
            <input class="rounded-md bg-slate-100 border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-slate-900 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-500" type="tel" name="phone" />
          </label>

          <label class="grid gap-2">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">Project Type *</span>
            <select class="rounded-md bg-slate-100 border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-slate-900 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-500" name="project_type" required>
              <option value="">Select a project type</option>
              <option value="website">Business Website</option>
              <option value="app">Web Application</option>
              <option value="ai">AI Solution</option>
              <option value="consulting">Consulting</option>
              <option value="training">Training</option>
              <option value="school">School Solution</option>
              <option value="other">Other</option>
            </select>
          </label>

          <label class="grid gap-2">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">Message *</span>
            <textarea class="rounded-md bg-slate-100 border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-slate-900 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-500" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Tell us about your project, goals, and timeline" required></textarea>
          </label>

          <button type="submit" class="w-full px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-sky-500 hover:bg-sky-400 text-slate-900 font-semibold transition-colors">
            Schedule Consultation
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <!-- Info Section -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-slate-900">What to Expect</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Clarify goals</strong> and success metrics for your project</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Understand challenges</strong> and current status</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Explore solutions</strong> tailored to your needs</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Discuss timeline</strong> and investment</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-slate-900">Quick Facts</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li>‚è±Ô∏è <strong>Duration:</strong> 30-45 minutes</li>
            <li>üí¨ <strong>Format:</strong> Video call or in-person (Lagos)</li>
            <li>üí∞ <strong>Cost:</strong> Completely free</li>
            <li>üìã <strong>Obligation:</strong> None - just a conversation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-sky-50 border border-sky-200 rounded-lg p-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-700">
            <strong>Prefer to chat first?</strong> Reach out on <a href="https://wa.me/2348163468669" class="text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 underline">WhatsApp</a> and we'll schedule a time that works for you.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
